Introduction

ARTBEAT v is a South Korean girl group formed by AB Creative and promoted under UniqueTunes Records. They made their debut on November 16, 2022 with the mini album "Magic". The members are part of the YouTube dance cover channel of the same name, ARTBEAT. On July 25, it was announced that the group will release their first single album, "Dubi Dubi". They also announced that ARTBEAT changed their name to ARTBEAT v, and that it will continue with 5 members, confirming Damhee's and Sieun's depature from the group.
